content:
To ensure that Analytics Integration users can view all the fields in the app, set field-level security for all the fields on all the objects that the app uses.

For more information on field-level security, see Salesforce field-level security.

To set field-level security for a field:

From Setup, enter the name of the object.
Select Fields & Relationships.
Select the field and Set Field-Level Security.
For the Analytics Cloud Integration User profile, select Visible and save changes.
title: Setting Field-Level Security for Analytics Integration Users
